[[File:Anna Maria Brizio.jpg|thumb|Anna Maria Brizio]] '''Anna Maria Brizio''' (1902-1982)<ref>[http://www.dwss.it/aics/i-personaggi-6/annamaria-brizio Annamaria Brizio (1902 - 1982).] Associazione Impegno Culturale. Retrieved 1 November 2017.</ref><ref>[http://www.lombardiabeniculturali.it/archivi/soggetti-produttori/persona/MIDC00098B/ Brizio Anna Maria.] Lombardia Beni Culturali. Retrieved 1 November 2017.</ref> was professor of [[art history]] at the [[University of Milan]], a member of the [[Commissione Vinciana]] and an authority on the work of [[Leonardo da Vinci]].
